flowchart TD
    A[OTA POST booking] --> B[Validasi X-API-Key]
    B --> C[Apply ApiKeyThrottlerGuard]
    C --> D[Validasi pickup/dropoff/tripCode]
    D --> E[Cek seat availability dan finalRate]
    E --> F[LockSeatService.createLockSeatService]
    F --> G[Buat Order status PENDING]
    G --> H[Permanent lock di DepartureAvailability]
    H --> I[Enqueue order-expired-queue 1 jam]
    I --> J[Enqueue unlock-seat-expired-queue 1 jam]
    J --> K[Return bookingCode + expiration_time + total_price]
    K --> L{OTA issuebooking sebelum expiry?}
    L -- Ya --> M[Create ticket by integration]
    M --> N[Order jadi PAID]
    N --> O[Sync DW report]
    L -- Tidak --> P[Worker expiry jalan]
    P --> Q[Order expire/cancel]
    Q --> R[Unlock seat availability]
